Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束在异世界 锡菲罗的心酸战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 龙咲海 与狮堂光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰寺风三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在充满回忆的东京塔 再度被召唤到锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企图得到锡菲罗的 欧多札姆 奇杰达 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个国家的军队 也进攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有另一个来路不明的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲着锡菲罗而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是迪波尼亚与 长得跟小光一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做新星的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在普蕾西雅的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光成功让剑复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与小风 也因为古列夫的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召回到城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候上空传来 迪波尼亚令人胆颤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第38话 伊格尔对锡菲罗城发动总攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都会跟着悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点输给自己时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于兰迪斯的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在创造室昏倒时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他送我到房间的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事时告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时可以帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 这孩子是何时溜出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特不知道有没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风的魔法治好他的伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特跑去救你 不就是白救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是 导师古列夫不知道怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从那么远的地方 让四个人瞬间移动…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他没问题 把我赶出了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 露出这么忧伤的少女面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会小海 你喜欢上 那个小孩外表的老爷爷啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魔法非常有效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果救了你们的人 却是导师古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在法连的龙中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我出去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的啦 我睡了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在门前监视 让你无法离开房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张床睡起来很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先攻下城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是去找古列夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你喜欢小光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不休息可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你…送我到房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有做什么奇怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的鸟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢小鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有支柱 花依然盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就算是在城堡里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的人们没有支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能创造出这么美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士 你是为何而战的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是亡母寄托给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这么重要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天它会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧多札姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉古那炮 准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉古那炮 预备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算击中城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是试探而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其突袭 不如受到盛大欢迎较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该先接近 确认一下会受到什么样的反击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真庆幸我不是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白焰防御
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防护罩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那也是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能以意志力来罩住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札兹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的技师精神 今天非常旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎样突破那个防护罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我检索了防护罩的精神能源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻击这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你到底 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的一击是挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是接下来还有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状况良好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要毫发无伤地回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FTO  GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GTO  GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟列斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 难得你能通过考验 让剑复活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你一直等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驭我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为自己的信念而战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于有小海跟小风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及相信我的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能够 再度跟大家一起作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在实际真正看到 感觉又更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用水的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重视速度甚于防御机能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用风的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重视防御甚于攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用火的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重视攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑的威力 是三具机器人中最强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先降低敌人防御力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
